title: 07/09/21 DPS Hour 2 Ryan Hollins
itunes:title: 07/09/21 DPS Hour 2 Ryan Hollins
description:
Jason Smith and Rob Parker fill in for Dan Patrick and say that Jose Altuve and Carlos Correa are hiding the real reason that they chose to skip the All-Star Game. 10-year NBA veteran Ryan Hollins stops by to share his thoughts on the NBA Finals and whether or not the series is already over. Plus, the guys debate who is the bigger MLB star: Shohei Ohtani or Fernando Tatis Jr.?
